INSERT INTO `cr_car_reviews` VALUES (1,'Great rental experience! Easy to drive and park The car was very reliable and had plenty of power when needed. The pickup process took a while but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,8,17,NULL,'published','2024-07-18 22:32:10','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(2,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! Exceptional craftsmanship and care Outstanding professionalism and care Best deal I\'ve found in years Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,14,80,NULL,'published','2024-10-06 21:13:59','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(3,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! Impeccable attention to every detail Exceptional attention to customer needs Worth every penny and more Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,23,91,NULL,'published','2024-08-06 04:16:35','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(4,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Incredibly comfortable for long drives Smooth acceleration and responsive braking Made our trip so much more enjoyable Only minor complaint is one of the USB ports wasn\'t working. Highly recommend!',4,32,46,NULL,'published','2024-11-02 20:26:19','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(5,'Excellent value for money. Excellent safety features gave us confidence Completely dependable for our entire trip Perfect companion for our business travel Will book with them again for sure.',4,12,58,NULL,'published','2024-09-30 02:46:37','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(6,'Standard rental car. The car was clean and functional Could use a bit more trunk space Meets expectations without exceeding them Met basic expectations.',3,22,98,NULL,'published','2025-10-03 11:10:31','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(7,'Outstanding rental experience! Surprisingly spacious for our family The car was absolutely pristine and handled like a dream on every road. The staff went above and beyond to help us Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,27,80,NULL,'published','2025-08-10 19:03:26','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(8,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Plenty of legroom for everyone Good handling in various driving conditions Handled the mountain roads beautifully Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,25,59,NULL,'published','2025-03-29 15:30:18','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(9,'Great rental experience! Great sound system The car was spotless inside and out and was very fuel efficient. Could use a bit more trunk space but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,6,16,NULL,'published','2025-06-29 08:20:04','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(10,'Below expectations. The GPS was a bit outdated The car was satisfactory for short trips but The pickup/return process. The staff was friendly enough but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,17,65,NULL,'published','2024-02-04 13:32:23','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(11,'Below expectations. Could use a bit more trunk space The car was reasonable considering the age but The vehicle\'s mechanical condition. The fuel economy was good but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,16,10,NULL,'published','2024-11-27 11:45:44','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(12,'Decent car for the price. The interior space was adequate one cup holder being a bit loose but overall acceptable for business trip. Would consider again if needed.',3,24,28,NULL,'published','2025-10-10 16:11:08','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(13,'Decent car for the price. The sound system worked fine a small scuff on the rear bumper but overall acceptable for conference. Would consider again if needed.',3,31,58,NULL,'published','2024-05-08 04:26:08','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(14,'Excellent value for money. The automatic climate control worked perfectly Never had a single mechanical issue Enhanced our weekend getaway experience Will book with them again for sure.',4,13,54,NULL,'published','2024-06-11 00:21:33','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(15,'Worst rental ever! The car broke down on the highway The car had transmission problems and I had to miss important appointments. Completely ruined my vacation. Avoid at all costs!',1,25,66,NULL,'published','2023-12-31 17:16:17','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(16,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Made the rental process seamless Perfect for business or leisure travel Just a small issue with a small scuff on the rear bumper but nothing major.',4,7,36,NULL,'published','2024-03-27 16:18:33','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(17,'Great rental experience! Smooth and quiet ride The car was in excellent mechanical condition and performed flawlessly throughout our trip. Could use a bit more trunk space but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,13,79,NULL,'published','2025-01-31 06:23:30','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(18,'Disappointing rental experience. The communication with staff was problematic and The brakes felt spongy and unsafe. Some good points but too many negatives.',2,26,24,NULL,'published','2025-11-03 02:38:37','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(19,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the technology features were helpful but the car showed some wear and tear. Standard rental experience Fair value for money.',3,6,38,NULL,'published','2024-03-12 13:49:11','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(20,'Absolutely fantastic! Premium features that enhanced every moment Performed flawlessly under all conditions Everything about this rental was perfect This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,22,83,NULL,'published','2023-12-11 11:45:46','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(21,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the comfort level was quite good but the vehicle felt a bit dated. Standard rental experience Fair value for money.',3,32,17,NULL,'published','2024-04-05 12:37:46','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(22,'Perfect car for our wedding! Unparalleled comfort for long-distance driving Exceptional driving dynamics in all conditions Service that sets the gold standard Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,22,100,NULL,'published','2025-08-18 22:17:52','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(23,'Great rental experience! Spacious interior The car was running smoothly and was very fuel efficient. Could use a bit more trunk space but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,7,71,NULL,'published','2024-02-28 16:56:38','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(24,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Made the rental process seamless Would definitely recommend to others Just a small issue with a small scuff on the rear bumper but nothing major.',4,5,10,NULL,'published','2024-09-21 05:22:00','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(25,'Outstanding rental experience! Incredible fuel efficiency saved us money The car was like driving a brand new car and exceeded all performance expectations. The team was absolutely wonderful to work with Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,10,44,NULL,'published','2024-05-24 21:03:56','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(26,'Great rental experience! Very comfortable seats The car was clean and well-maintained and was very fuel efficient. Could use a bit more trunk space but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,18,91,NULL,'published','2024-07-27 09:19:56','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(27,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Quick and easy pickup process Would definitely recommend to others Just a small issue with one cup holder being a bit loose but nothing major.',4,32,85,NULL,'published','2025-01-24 16:22:42','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(28,'Absolutely fantastic! Premium features that enhanced every moment Not a single issue throughout our entire rental This rental exceeded every expectation This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,13,71,NULL,'published','2024-04-14 00:34:02','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(29,'Absolutely fantastic! The technology was cutting-edge and intuitive Not a single issue throughout our entire rental A truly exceptional experience from start to finish This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,17,30,NULL,'published','2025-03-19 06:26:50','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(30,'Terrible experience with this car. The interior was dirty and smelled bad The vehicle was showing significant wear and was not as described. Would not recommend to anyone. Customer service was unhelpful when I reported the issues.',1,24,89,NULL,'published','2025-05-11 02:10:49','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(31,'Great rental experience! Smooth and quiet ride The car was clean and well-maintained and performed flawlessly throughout our trip. The radio presets weren\'t cleared but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,10,83,NULL,'published','2025-04-21 21:11:15','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(32,'Average rental experience. Nothing particularly stood out about this rental The GPS was a bit outdated but the fuel efficiency was decent. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,5,24,NULL,'published','2024-06-10 17:28:25','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(33,'Had some issues with this rental. The radio kept cutting out making the trip uncomfortable in hot weather The price was reasonable but the quality didn\'t match.',2,13,37,NULL,'published','2024-03-21 15:27:13','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(34,'Disappointing rental experience. The overall value proposition was problematic and The interior was dirty and smelled bad. Some good points but too many negatives.',2,1,92,NULL,'published','2024-09-13 19:34:47','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(35,'Excellent value for money. The infotainment system was user-friendly Never had a single mechanical issue Enhanced our weekend getaway experience Will book with them again for sure.',4,27,73,NULL,'published','2024-03-09 20:01:01','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(36,'Below expectations. Could use a bit more trunk space The car was acceptable but not impressive but The vehicle\'s mechanical condition. The staff was friendly enough but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,16,24,NULL,'published','2024-02-27 01:17:29','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(37,'Not great but manageable. The ride quality was rougher than expected The car started reliably Would look for other options next time.',2,5,69,NULL,'published','2024-06-26 19:11:33','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(38,'Below expectations. The pickup process took a while The car was acceptable but not impressive but The communication with staff. The pickup process was smooth but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,17,36,NULL,'published','2024-01-18 17:32:17','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(39,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable Smooth acceleration and responsive braking Perfect for our family vacation Only minor complaint is one of the USB ports wasn\'t working. Highly recommend!',4,18,20,NULL,'published','2023-11-30 03:08:15','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(40,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Very helpful with directions Great choice for anyone needing a reliable car Just a small issue with the pickup location being slightly hard to find but nothing major.',4,25,61,NULL,'published','2024-09-25 00:09:05','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(41,'Outstanding rental experience! Incredible fuel efficiency saved us money The car was immaculate in every detail and exceeded all performance expectations. The staff went above and beyond to help us Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,27,63,NULL,'published','2024-12-31 13:25:25','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(42,'Absolutely fantastic! Advanced capabilities that impressed everyone Absolutely perfect reliability record The best rental car experience we\'ve ever had This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,29,40,NULL,'published','2024-01-11 19:25:44','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(43,'Outstanding rental experience! Surprisingly spacious for our family The car was showroom quality and delivered outstanding fuel economy. The team was absolutely wonderful to work with Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,12,77,NULL,'published','2024-11-29 18:57:30','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(44,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Excellent customer service Will be my go-to rental company Just a small issue with a small scuff on the rear bumper but nothing major.',4,15,36,NULL,'published','2025-07-28 12:06:51','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(45,'Outstanding rental experience! Whisper-quiet cabin and smooth ride The car was showroom quality and exceeded all performance expectations. The staff went above and beyond to help us Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,30,55,NULL,'published','2025-09-16 14:18:52','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(46,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! The quality was absolutely pristine Staff went above and beyond at every step Incredible bang for your buck Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,8,8,NULL,'published','2025-05-31 01:32:58','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(47,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! Impeccable attention to every detail Outstanding professionalism and care Premium experience at a fair price Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,3,81,NULL,'published','2024-04-30 01:39:26','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(48,'Very pleased with this rental. Attention to detail was evident throughout Very helpful with directions Great choice for anyone needing a reliable car Just a small issue with one cup holder being a bit loose but nothing major.',4,24,49,NULL,'published','2024-10-25 11:35:11','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(49,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the fuel economy exceeded expectations but the customer service could be improved. Does what it\'s supposed to do Fair value for money.',3,1,98,NULL,'published','2024-10-17 13:04:53','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(50,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable The engine performed well on both city and highway Great for city driving and parking Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,29,90,NULL,'published','2024-02-10 11:15:47','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(51,'Absolutely fantastic! Premium features that enhanced every moment Performed flawlessly under all conditions Absolutely outstanding in every possible way This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,30,21,NULL,'published','2025-05-07 02:25:12','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(52,'Below expectations. The radio presets weren\'t cleared The car was acceptable but not impressive but The pickup/return process. The fuel economy was good but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,9,100,NULL,'published','2025-08-04 00:12:33','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(53,'Excellent value for money. The keyless entry was very convenient No unexpected problems or breakdowns Contributed to a memorable road trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,3,46,NULL,'published','2024-12-13 20:05:49','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(54,'Below expectations. The GPS was a bit outdated The car was adequate for the price point but The vehicle\'s mechanical condition. The fuel economy was good but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,26,97,NULL,'published','2024-12-08 22:55:35','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(55,'Perfect car for our business trip! The seats were like luxury recliners The performance was absolutely flawless Staff went above and beyond at every step Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,19,9,NULL,'published','2024-08-09 17:02:35','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(56,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! The quality was absolutely pristine The customer service was world-class Best deal I\'ve found in years Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,7,59,NULL,'published','2025-07-27 10:36:12','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(57,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Climate control worked perfectly Reliable performance throughout our trip Great for city driving and parking Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,16,37,NULL,'published','2024-02-05 11:47:51','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(58,'Had some issues with this rental. The radio kept cutting out that was quite annoying during the drive The price was reasonable but the quality didn\'t match.',2,24,37,NULL,'published','2024-01-20 07:30:23','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(59,'Decent car for the price. The interior space was adequate one cup holder being a bit loose but overall acceptable for family road trip. Would consider again if needed.',3,21,77,NULL,'published','2024-10-13 23:23:47','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(60,'Great rental experience! Great sound system The car was in excellent mechanical condition and had plenty of power when needed. Could use a bit more trunk space but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,24,59,NULL,'published','2025-11-01 06:44:38','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(61,'Standard rental car. The car was clean and functional The GPS was a bit outdated Nothing exceptional but nothing terrible Met basic expectations.',3,24,99,NULL,'published','2024-09-28 10:41:24','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(62,'Excellent value for money. Excellent safety features gave us confidence Started every time without hesitation Made our vacation stress-free and enjoyable Will book with them again for sure.',4,21,75,NULL,'published','2024-03-17 07:42:18','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(63,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! Luxury-level quality throughout Exceptional attention to customer needs Premium experience at a fair price Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,32,90,NULL,'published','2025-05-09 07:26:53','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(64,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Climate control worked perfectly Reliable performance throughout our trip Impressed all our passengers Only minor complaint is the return process was slightly confusing. Highly recommend!',4,3,1,NULL,'published','2024-04-24 23:12:02','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(65,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Excellent customer service Perfect for business or leisure travel Just a small issue with the owner\'s manual being missing but nothing major.',4,18,3,NULL,'published','2024-11-12 11:49:16','2025-11-27 20:07:30'),(66,'Perfect car for our wedding! Premium seating that rivals luxury vehicles Exceptional driving dynamics in all conditions Staff went above and beyond at every step Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,21,89,NULL,'published','2025-11-08 23:56:59','2025-11-27 20:07:30');
