ur sed libero.',0,0,'galleries/8.jpg',1,'published','2025-11-27 20:06:25','2025-11-27 20:06:25'),(9,'The Future of Electric and Hybrid Cars','Et distinctio porro accusantium qui impedit ipsa. Rerum iure est aperiam iste fugiat. Eaque similique ipsum velit iusto enim illo id.',0,0,'galleries/9.jpg',1,'published','2025-11-27 20:06:25','2025-11-27 20:06:25'),(10,'Luxury Car Interiors: A Closer Look','Voluptatem maiores rerum neque eum. Et consequuntur sunt corrupti ipsum nihil facere labore aut. Id dolor exercitationem possimus eaque.',0,0,'galleries/10.jpg',1,'published','2025-11-27 20:06:25','2025-11-27 20:06:25');
